ca.groceriestogo.model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.groceriestogo.model.User

  • @Entity
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    The User class is a model representing the users of the system. This is a database entity and represents the user table in the database.
    Version:
    1.0 (2022-02-12)
    Author:
    Daniel Hinbest, Ryan Clayson, Yash Gadhiya
